        public TemplateState.Builder templateYaml​(@Nullable
                                          com.pulumi.core.Output<java.lang.String> templateYaml)
        Parameters:
        templateYaml - Yaml for creating new Template. In YAML, to reference an entity at the organization scope, prefix 'org' to the expression: org.{identifier}. To reference an entity at the account scope, prefix 'account` to the expression: account.{identifier}. For eg, to reference a connector with identifier 'connectorId' at the organization scope in a stage mention it as connectorRef: org.connectorId.
